dct_title_s: Graecia cum insulis et oris maris Aegaei
dct_description_sm: Cover title: Griechenland mit den Inseln und Küsten des Aegäischen Meeres. Relief shown by hachures. Inset: Troas et Hellespontus duplici maioris tabulae modulo. At head of map: Atlas antiquus, tab. V. Originally issued in Kiepert's Atlas antiquus, first published in 1859. Originally issued folded to 19 x 12 cm.
